</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[189,1399,678,777]" box="[197,1399,750,777]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<keyLead box="[197,1399,750,777]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
– Ep3 with posteroventral tooth only (posterior border rounded) (
<figureCitation box="[962,1053,750,776]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="12.[189,232,1930,1956]" captionTargetBox="[217,1370,265,1890]" captionTargetId="figure@12.[217,1371,265,1890]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="Fig. 7. Halirages cainae sp. nov., holotype ♂, 40 mm, Norwegian Sea, MAREANO 2009-111, R-station 487, sample 157. A. pleonite 1. B. pleonite 2. C. pleonite 3. D. ventrolateral part of urosomite 1 and right U1 (apical cluster of spines of outer ramus drawn after left U1). E. left U2. F. right U3." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3857951" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3857951/files/figure.png" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Fig. 7C</figureCitation>
)........................................... 4
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<paragraph blockId="25.[189,1399,816,879]" box="[189,1399,816,842]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<keyLead box="[189,1399,816,842]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">2. Pereionite 7 with 0-1 posterodorsal tooth; pleonite 1 and 2 with 1 posterodorsal tooth ..................... 3</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[189,1399,816,879]" box="[197,1399,851,879]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<keyLead box="[197,1399,851,879]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
