<emphasis bold="true" box="[1032,1194,1827,1854]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">H. gorbunovi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gurjanova E. F." box="[1201,1399,1827,1853]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="272 - 297" refId="ref13791" refString="Gurjanova E. F. 1946. New species of Isopoda and Amphipoda from the Arctic Ocean. Transactions of the Drifting Expedition of the Main Administration of the Northern Sea Route on the Icebreaker &quot; Sedov &quot;, 1937 - 1940 3: 272 - 297 (in Russian)." type="journal article" year="1946">Gurjanova, 1946</bibRefCitation>
