<keyLead box="[196,1399,1863,1890]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
– Ventral border of coxa 1-2 smooth or nearly so...................................... 
<taxonomicName authority="Kamenskaya, 1980" authorityName="Kamenskaya" authorityYear="1980" box="[1047,1399,1863,1890]" class="Malacostraca" family="Calliopiidae" genus="Halirages" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="caecus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1047,1166,1864,1890]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">H. caecus</emphasis>
